    <item>
      <title>Version 1.0.88</title>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>What's New in 1.0.88</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Preview default 100% zoom + thumbnail aspect fit in rounded rect</li>
          <li>Image preview too small for wide/short images — fixed</li>
          <li>Image thumbnail overflow in search results — fixed</li>
          <li>RAW preview loading + video thumbnails optimized</li>
          <li>Video preview with zoom/pan + play controls + trackpad pinch</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
